@startuml DiceManager

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam classFontStyle bold
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam nodesep 50
skinparam ranksep 30

title Diagram Kelas DiceManager

class DiceManager {
    - die1 : int
    - die2 : int
    __
    + DiceManager()
    + rollRandom() : pair<int, int>
    + setManual(d1 : int, d2 : int) : void
    + getDie1() : int
    + getDie2() : int
    + getTotal() : int
    + isDouble() : bool
}

note right of DiceManager
    <b>Mengelola 2 dadu bersisi 6 (2d6)</b>

    <b>rollRandom():</b>
    die1 = rand(1..6), die2 = rand(1..6)
    return {die1, die2}

    <b>setManual(d1, d2):</b>
    Validasi 1 ≤ d1,d2 ≤ 6
    Untuk perintah ATUR_DADU X Y

    <b>isDouble():</b>
    return die1 == die2

    <b>getTotal():</b>
    return die1 + die2
    Digunakan oleh:
    · TurnManager → processMovement
    · Game → setLastDiceTotal (untuk sewa Utility)

    <b>Digunakan oleh:</b> GameEngine
    (saat LEMPAR_DADU atau ATUR_DADU)
end note

@enduml
